title: Biden Slidin’, Too Many Tens 2.19.20

description:
In episode 572, Jack and Miles are joined by Couples Therapy podcast's Andy Beckerman to discuss All Star Weekend, a check in with the polls, Subway's new deal, Boy Scouts of America filing for bankruptcy, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. NBA All-Star Weekend Winners and Losers: New All-Star Game format shines; Aaron Gordon robbed again
  2. Sanders opens 12-point lead nationally: poll
  3. Subway’s latest deal great for customers, potentially disastrous for franchise owners
  4. Boy Scouts of America Files for Bankruptcy After Surge in Sex Abuse Lawsuits
  5. WATCH: Drugdealer - Suddenly
